(13, 51, 11, '<p>øyvind nystad</p>', '<p>creative director</p>', '<h1>Create the dream</h1>\n<h2>it''s about doing the unexpected and to amuse - at any time.</h2>\n<p>The perfect store, an artistic vision, the ultimate design, filled with dreams to inspire, incite and entertain.</p>\n<p>But a beautiful shopping experience is not enough. For a store to be successful the retail design must express the soul of the brand-that is the brand´s values and strength. Striking the right balance among the products,  communication, design, architecture and education is the only way to achieve this goal. As an retail designer, you need a unique mix of elements for each projects, because every brands develops differently. Ultimate shopping experience is a place driven by passion and experience. You can have a fantastically designed store, but if the owners and staff aren´t  fully behind it, it will never work. Fantastic opportunities exist for imaginative retailers.</p>\n<p>Today retail design has to update and to adapt the appearance of the retail space regularly, so that each new collection can be displayed in a fresh way.</p>', '<p>Øyvind is the</p>', '<p>+47 911 78 924</p>', '<p>oyvind@reactorretail.com</p>', 22),
