(26, 51, 18, '<p>stein berg</p>', '<p>senior retail designer</p>', '<h1>Create the dream</h1>\n<h2>do the unexpected - all the time</h2>\n<p>The perfect store, an artistic vision, the ultimate design, filled with dreams to inspire, incite and entertain. But a beautiful shopping experience is not enough.</p>\n<p>For a store to be successful the retail design must express the soul of the brand-that is the brand´s values and strength. Striking the right balance among the products,  communication, design, architecture and education is the only way to achieve this goal. As an retail designer, you need a unique mix of elements for each projects, because every brands develops differently. Ultimate shopping experience is a place driven by passion and experience. You can have a fantastically designed store, but if the owners and staff aren´t  fully behind it, it will never work. Fantastic opportunities exist for imaginative retailers.</p>', '<p>Stein Berg is an well skilled retail designer and shop planner with more than 30 years of retail and concept development experience, and with hundred of thousands square meter retail space planned and behind visual expression for a wide range of brands as Stokke, Statoil, Bohus, Ikea, Steen &amp; Strøm, Lefdal, Gresvig, Varnergruppen, Oslo Airport, ARG, Dressmann, Apotek 1, Moods of Norway, Marbodal, Coop and many more. </p>', '<p>+47 917 58 805</p>', '<p>seb@reactorretail.com</p>', 22),
(27, 51, 19, '<p>stein berg</p>', '<p>senior retail designer</p>', '<h1>Create the dream</h1>\n<h2>do the unexpected - all the time</h2>\n<p>The perfect store, an artistic vision, the ultimate design, filled with dreams to inspire, incite and entertain. But a beautiful shopping experience is not enough. For a store to be successful the retail design must express the soul of the brand-that is the brand´s values and strength. Striking the right balance among the products,  communication, design, architecture and education is the only way to achieve this goal. As an retail designer, you need a unique mix of elements for each projects, because every brands develops differently. Ultimate shopping experience is a place driven by passion and experience. You can have a fantastically designed store, but if the owners and staff aren´t  fully behind it, it will never work. Fantastic opportunities exist for imaginative retailers.</p>', '<p>Stein Berg is an well skilled retail designer and shop planner with more than 30 years of retail and concept development experience, and with hundred of thousands square meter retail space planned and behind visual expression for a wide range of brands as Stokke, Statoil, Bohus, Ikea, Steen &amp; Strøm, Lefdal, Gresvig, Varnergruppen, Oslo Airport, ARG, Dressmann, Apotek 1, Moods of Norway, Marbodal, Coop and many more. </p>', '<p>+47 917 58 805</p>', '<p>seb@reactorretail.com</p>', 22),
(28, 6, 3, '<p>dag landewall</p>', '<p>Senior advisor brands &amp; retail</p>', '<h1>Cave men</h1>\n<h2>in a big data world.</h2>\n<p>Humans are and will always be very social herd animals. We need real life places to meet and yes, shopping is a very much social activity. And like it or not – the most of our shopping is not based on rational needs. We are building our own identity through our choices of products, brands and services. Our aspirations, hopes and desires are the real drivers in most of our consumption, not rational cost/benefit calculations.</p>\n<h3>Make more mistakes. Faster!</h3>\n<p>The winners of tomorrow are thriving on this uncertainty, creating game changing opportunities through a culture of fast and vigilant experimenting. Don’t work? Good, then we know that. Test something else. Work? Good, get it out there – now.</p>', '<p>Dag Landewall is the co-founder of Reactor and has over 30 years of retail and concept development experience.<br> In addition to chair Reactor Retail and Reactor Products he’s advising select corporate clients on retail, concept and brand strategy issues.<br> He’s an expert in developing compelling, consumer relevant and to-the-point brand stories, brand values and personalities.</p>', '<p>+47 952 12 345</p>', '<p><a href="mailto:dag@reactorretail.com">dag@reactorretail.com</a></p>', 4),
