(54, 51, 20, '<p>stein berg</p>', '<p>senior retail designer</p>', '<h1>Creating the dream</h1>\n<h2>be surprising-all the time</h2>\n<p>The perfect store, an artistic vision, the ultimate design, filled with dreams to inspire, incite and entertain. But a beautiful shopping experience is not enough. For a store to be successful the retail design must express the soul of the brand-that is the brand´s values and strength. Striking the right balance among the products,  communication, design, architecture and education is the only way to achieve this goal. As an retail designer, you need a unique mix of elements for each projects, because every brands develops differently. Ultimate shopping experience is a place driven by passion and experience. You can have a fantastically designed store, but if the owners and staff aren´t  fully behind it, it will never work. Fantastic opportunities exist for imaginative retailers.</p>', '<p>Stein Berg is an well skilled retail designer and shop planner with more than 30 years of retail and concept development experience, and with hundred of thousands square meter retail space planned and behind visual expression for a wide range of brands as Stokke, Statoil, Bohus, Ikea, Steen &amp; Strøm, Lefdal, Gresvig, Varnergruppen, Oslo Airport, ARG, Dressmann, Apotek 1, Moods of Norway, Marbodal, Coop and many more. </p>', '<p>+47 917 58 805</p>', '<p>seb@reactorretail.com</p>', 22),
(55, 51, 21, '<p>stein berg</p>', '<p>senior retail designer</p>', '<h1>Creating the dream</h1>\n<h2>never stop surprising</h2>\n<p>The perfect store, an artistic vision, the ultimate design, filled with dreams to inspire, incite and entertain. But a beautiful shopping experience is not enough. For a store to be successful the retail design must express the soul of the brand-that is the brand´s values and strength. Striking the right balance among the products,  communication, design, architecture and education is the only way to achieve this goal. As an retail designer, you need a unique mix of elements for each projects, because every brands develops differently. Ultimate shopping experience is a place driven by passion and experience. You can have a fantastically designed store, but if the owners and staff aren´t  fully behind it, it will never work. Fantastic opportunities exist for imaginative retailers.</p>', '<p>Stein Berg is an well skilled retail designer and shop planner with more than 30 years of retail and concept development experience, and with hundred of thousands square meter retail space planned and behind visual expression for a wide range of brands as Stokke, Statoil, Bohus, Ikea, Steen &amp; Strøm, Lefdal, Gresvig, Varnergruppen, Oslo Airport, ARG, Dressmann, Apotek 1, Moods of Norway, Marbodal, Coop and many more. </p>', '<p>+47 917 58 805</p>', '<p>seb@reactorretail.com</p>', 22),
