(234, 78, 22, '<p>brand idenity design</p>', '<p>hilde steen aamodt</p>', '<h1>gold diggers</h1>\n<p>Excellent visual expressions of brands are mostly based on the company''s own DNA and are able to tell the history, aspirations and vision of thebrand in a condensed form. I believe in cultivating the client company''s personal traits, characteristics and values  to its full potential and prefer to creating the identity from within, based on visual translations of strategic insights rather than to base it on design trends.  My experience is that this approach results in extended longlivety for the brand and that it also will generate greater pride and internal ownership. Also, idenitites created from within are often perceived as more unique and trustworthy in the marketplace. Therefore our approach is that every company and brand has a golden ore to be discovered - and our job is to find that ore and make sustainable brandwork out of it.</p>', '<p>Hilde Steen Aamodt, Senior Graphic Designer, has 20 years of experience in advertising and graphic design, the last 10 years with a focus on the development of brand identities. She has won the National Award for Design twice, and earned the reputation of being one of the most skilled graphic designers in Scandinavia.</p>', '<p>(+47) 900 39 019</p>', '<p>hilde@reactorretail.com</p>', 260),
