(247, 80, 21, '<p>sourcing, piloting &amp; roll-outs</p>', '<p>erik huseby</p>', '<h1>big ideas </h1>\n<h2>into the real world</h2>\n<p>In the disruptive and unpredictable market of today, companies has a ever decreasing window of opportunity to bring their new brand, offer or concept into the marketplace. There is an increasing risk that a great idea will become irrelevant before it reaches the marketplace.</p>\n<p>I believe in limiting the time used between the creating of the big idea and it''s first meeting with real live customers. Speeding up the process..</p>\n<p>Therefore our approach is to prepare the concepts we develop for implementation in parallell with the ideation and conception of the  ideas What is a good idea? One that''s done is. If not, its not. </p>\n<p>Vi...</p>', '<p>Erik Huseby leads our work with bringing the concepts we create into the real world through sourcing, piloting and roll-out management. As a leading shop fitting authority he also manages tender and hardware sourcing processes for select retail clients.   </p>', '<p>+47 916 86 244</p>', '<p>erik@reactorretail.com</p>', 264),
