(287, 78, 33, '<p>brand idenity design</p>', '<p>hilde steen aamodt</p>', '<h1>gold diggers</h1>\n<p>Excellent visual expressions of brands are mostly based on the company''s own DNA and are able to tell the history, aspirations and vision of the brand in a condensed form.</p>\n<p>I believe in cultivating the client company''s personal traits, characteristics and values to its full potential and prefer creating the identity from within, based on visual translations of strategic insights rather than to base it on design trends. My experience is that this approach results in extended longevity for the brand and that it also generates greater pride and internal ownership. In addition, idenitites created from within are often perceived as more unique and trustworthy in the marketplace.</p>\n<p>Consequently, our approach is that every company and brand possesses gold ore waiting to be discovered - and our job is to find that ore and make sustainable brandwork out of it.</p>', '<p>Hilde Steen Aamodt, Senior Graphic Designer, is a highly experienced graphic designer. In addition to creating commercially successful identities, she creates complete design programs and guidelines, brand &amp; in-store communication, editorial design and advertising. Hilde is behind the visual expression for a wide range of brand designs i.e. Nille, Jøtul, Match, Voice, Regatta, Printz, Lefdal, Eurosko, Gyldendal, Tiden and Miles.</p>\n<p>Her work has been awarded The Award for Design Excellence.</p>', '<p>(+47) 900 39 019</p>', '<p>hilde@reactorretail.com</p>', 260),
