(1, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 21:59:48', '2015-04-13 07:31:36', 'An entire new dimension was added to Swedish sausage culture in 2013 when the Printz restaurant opened in Stockholm’s own meatpacking district, Slakthusområdet. Together with  the innovator, gastronome and restaurateur, Ricard Constantinou, we created a tribute to the district’s centuries-old sausage tradition. The beer hall. Photograph by Märta Thisner.\r\n', 10, 86, 0),
(2, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 22:00:01', '2015-03-23 08:14:35', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. A total of 25 locally brewed beers on tap. Photograph by Märta Thisner.', 10, 87, 0),
(3, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 22:00:12', '2015-03-23 08:14:52', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. The making and serving of Printz signature delicatessen sausages. Photograph by Märta Thisner.', 10, 62, 0),
(4, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 22:00:42', '2015-04-14 17:06:17', 'We created the Printz brand and visual identity program, including the logo program, design elements, \r\npackaging and graphic templates. Entrance identity sign.', 11, 310, 0),
(5, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 22:00:54', '2015-04-14 17:13:15', 'We created the Printz brand and visual identity program, including the logo program, design elements, \r\npackaging and graphic templates. One sheet from our sketchbook showing early work based on a brief that shows the \r\nSwedish heritage of nobility from the early 20th century.', 11, 311, 0),
(6, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 22:01:05', '2015-04-14 17:09:32', 'We created the Printz brand and visual identity program, including the logo program, design elements, \r\npackaging and graphic templates. These are the main graphic elements containing the logotype, symbols, the pattern of sausages, typography, colors and photo direction.', 11, 312, 0),
(7, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-26 22:01:25', '2015-04-14 17:10:36', 'We created the Printz brand and visual identity program, including the logo program, design elements, packaging and graphic templates. Printz has seven different departments that are diffentiated by their own symbol and color.', 11, 313, 0),
(9, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 11:54:03', '2015-03-23 08:15:09', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. The fine dining. Photograph by Märta Thisner.', 10, 64, 0),
