(12, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:19:36', '2015-03-23 08:14:09', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. The butcher and his meat-hanging and curing rooms. Photographs by Märta Thisner.', 10, 67, 0),
