(16, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:22:22', '2015-03-23 08:17:01', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. The microbrewery and what comes out of it. Photographs by Märta Thisner.', 10, 70, 0),
(17, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:22:42', '2015-03-23 08:17:27', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. Die Bierstube. Photograph by Märta Thisner.', 10, 71, 0),
(18, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:23:07', '2015-03-23 08:17:52', 'Printz is  Sweden’s first delicatessen sausage restaurant featuring in-house sausage-making, a beer & food hall, fine dining and a microbrewery. The wine cellar. Photograph by Märta Thisner.', 10, 72, 0),
(19, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:36:53', '2015-04-13 14:00:23', 'Although Stockholm has developed some interesting restaurants over the past 10 to 15 years, there have been\r\n no exciting developments involving the food hall concept. So when a classic Stockholm commercial space in Kungsgatan became available, Ricard Constantinou, our client and one of the leading restaurant entrepreneurs in Sweden, \r\nmoved in to fill that gap in the food hall market. ', 13, 74, 0),
(20, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:37:42', '2015-04-13 14:00:59', 'The customers at K25, many of whom come from nearby offices, have access to a dozen high-quality businesses selling food. \r\nThere are ten restaurants plus a coffee shop. Food options include sushi, Italian, Greek & Turkish food, Chinese dumplings and a classic Swedish delicatessen from Lisa Elmqvist and Lilla Vigårda. ', 13, 92, 0),
(21, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:38:23', '2015-04-13 14:02:09', 'The customers at K25, many of whom come from nearby offices, have access to a dozen high-quality businesses selling food. \r\nThere are ten restaurants plus a coffee shop. Food options include sushi, Italian, Greek & Turkish food, Chinese dumplings and a classic Swedish delicatessen from Lisa Elmqvist and Lilla Vigårda. ', 13, 93, 0),
(22, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 12:39:22', '2015-03-23 08:41:47', 'We designed and planned the entire interior to create a clear differentiation between the different participating restaurant concepts while also securing an overall consistent design language. \r\n', 13, 94, 0),
(23, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 14:41:56', '2015-04-13 14:40:11', 'Retail concept design, identity and communications work for Interfoto, Norway’s premier professional photography outfitter \r\nsince 1966. We converted an old industrial building in Oslo into a combined flagship store, showroom, training facility and head office, creating a premier destination for professional photographers and dedicated amateurs alike. \r\n', 18, 124, 0),
(24, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 14:49:58', '2015-04-13 14:40:21', 'Retail concept design, identity and communications work for Interfoto, Norway’s premier professional photography outfitter \r\nsince 1966. Interfoto flagship store in Oslo. Shop-in-shops for Nikon & Canon.', 18, 125, 0),
(25, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 14:50:19', '2015-04-13 14:40:32', 'Retail concept design, identity and communications work for Interfoto, Norway’s premier professional photography outfitter \r\nsince 1966. Interfoto flagship store in Oslo. The in-store library and café lounge.', 18, 126, 0),
(26, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 14:50:45', '2015-04-13 14:40:44', 'Retail concept design, identity and communications work for Interfoto, Norway’s premier professional photography outfitter \r\nsince 1966. Interfoto flagship store in Oslo. Photo lighting department. ', 18, 127, 0),
(27, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 14:51:14', '2015-04-13 14:40:57', 'Retail concept design, identity and communications work for Interfoto, Norway’s premier professional photography outfitter \r\nsince 1966. Interfoto flagship store in Oslo. Hasselblad shop-in-shop.', 18, 128, 0),
(28, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 14:51:54', '2015-04-13 14:41:07', 'Retail concept design, identity and communications work for Interfoto, Norway’s premier professional photography outfitter \r\nsince 1966. Interfoto flagship store in Oslo. In-store service cubicle.', 18, 129, 0),
