(34, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:25:04', '2015-04-13 22:18:21', 'This is what you meet at the entrance to the studio building in which Reactor is housed on the top floor. It functions \r\nas a combined reception area for the building and coffee bar for residents, visitors, and bypassers. Brenneriet is a joint pro bono social entrepreneurial project from Reactor, Anthon B.Nilsen and the City of Oslo, giving young people with special needs an opportunity to enter the job market and build self-esteem with a real job. ', 21, 38, 0),
(35, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:25:38', '2015-03-11 16:29:56', 'The interior concept is rustic and robust to reflect the old, industrial surroundings. The graphic design combines the traditional and the urban, and gives the BR5 coffee bar a strong modern identity.', 21, 137, 0),
(36, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:27:37', '2015-02-27 15:30:10', 'Brenneriet is joint pro-bono social entrepreneurial project from Reactor, Anthon B.Nilsen and The City of Oslo, that gives young people with special needs an opportunity to enter the job market and building self asteem with a real job. ', 22, 0, 0),
(37, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:33:41', '2015-04-14 06:50:58', 'Nille is Norway’s leading discount home decorating  chain. As is the case with many retailers in the same category, smartness and attractiveness were not the first things that came to mind. In connection with the chain''s plans to expand into Sweden, we redesigned their visual identity and rethought their brand story and values. Since the Nille rebranding and redesign work, Nille has successfully entered the Swedish market with 30 stores and also been awarded the "Norwegian Store of the Year" prize.', 24, 318, 0),
(38, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:34:44', '2015-02-27 15:34:49', 'In addition, we created a new retail concept and communication concept. We maintained the discount persona, but with an added smartness factor. The first couple of stores are now opened in Sweden and the new identity is under a step-by-step implementation in different media. Discount is already smart, but may also be pretty. ', 25, 0, 0),
(39, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:37:29', '2015-02-27 15:37:29', 'In connection with the 2013 merger between the two Swedish pharmacy chains; Kronans Droghandel and MedStop, we created a new brand, visual identity and in-store communication program. The chain now operates over 200 pharmacies across Sweden under the new Kronans Apotek banner. ', 27, 0, 0),
(40, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:38:46', '2015-02-27 15:38:50', 'Brand creation and complete visual identity design program. New brand symbol and logotype for Kronans Apotek.', 27, 0, 0),
(41, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:39:16', '2015-02-27 15:39:18', 'Brand creation and complete visual identity design program. New facade signage designs for all new and rebranded stores. ', 27, 0, 0),
(42, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:40:12', '2015-02-27 15:40:15', 'Concept development, retail design and visual merchandising works for Kronans Apotek. \r\nKronans Apotek at Stockholm Central Station.', 28, 0, 0),
(43, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:40:51', '2015-02-27 15:40:54', 'Concept development, retail design and visual meerchandising works for Kronans Apotek. \r\nDesign and implementation of cosmetics category display in select stores.', 28, 0, 0),
(44, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:42:58', '2015-03-13 06:56:20', 'Branding work for Regatta, a global leader in professional off-shore life-saving and flotation equipment. Following a strategy to expand the brand into new categories, we developed a new brand story based on it’s Norwegian north sea heritage. We then created a complete visual identity, design program and guidelines for collection design, brand communication, stationery and advertising.', 30, 148, 0),
(45, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:55:59', '2015-05-18 12:11:40', 'Visual identity, graphic design program, architecture and design guidelines for Ingo, the new name for the former Jet brand discount fuel station network in Sweden and Denmark that is now owned by Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. Ingo site in Sweden. ', 36, 289, 3),
(46, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 15:59:56', '2015-04-13 08:01:26', 'New retail concept for Synsam including strategy, retail design, store planning and in-store communications. Under implementation across Norway. Synsam flagship store in Stavanger. Photo by Daniel Tengs.', 38, 116, 0),
(47, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 16:00:58', '2015-04-13 08:01:41', 'New retail concept for Synsam including strategy, retail design, store planning and in-store communications. Under implementation across Norway. Synsam flagship store in Stavanger. Photo by Daniel Tengs.', 38, 96, 0),
(48, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 16:02:18', '2015-04-13 13:41:07', 'New brand identity and signage design for Synsam for use at all store locations where the new retail concept for Synsam \r\nis being implemented. Main identity sign.', 39, 383, 0),
(49, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 16:03:16', '2015-03-23 08:54:17', 'Art direction, copywriting and design for Synsam customer magazine, with 1 million copies distributed 6-8 times per year across Norway. Its provocative approach has stirred some debate but has also yielded significant commercial success and marketing awards. Photographs by Morten Quale.', 40, 102, 0),
(50, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 16:04:08', '2015-03-23 08:54:52', 'Art direction, copywriting and design for on-going Synsam promotions. Billboard campaign. ', 41, 105, 0),
(51, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 16:04:35', '2015-03-23 08:55:04', 'Art direction, copywriting and design for on-going Synsam promotions. Billboard campaign. ', 41, 106, 0),
(52, 'Slideshow', '2015-02-27 16:10:19', '2015-04-14 16:55:08', 'Voice is a Norwegian fashion group operating the Match, VIC and Boys chain stores in Norway. In addition, \r\nthey house a number of fashion brands and private label collections. We developed a new brand identity for Voice that will mainly be used in B2B relations as the respective chains are using their own identities towards the market. This is the new logo and one of the images in the corporate image series containing different situations from studio photoshoots in a neutral and timeless style. \r\nPhoto: Henrik Beck Kæmpe/Reactor.  Model: Madelaine Borgersen Kjørren', 43, 108, 0),
