(35, 7, 12, '<h5 style="text-align: justify;">Graphic Designer, Therese Skjenken (left) working out the design details for Miles, the new fuel brand for Statoil, together with Project Manager, Hedi Nielsen (right). The Miles design program will be applied onto over 50 different pumps and ranging.</h5>\n<h1>miles for statoil</h1>\n<h6>By Øyvind Nystad</h6>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Statoil Fuel &amp; Retail is the leading service station chain in northern Europe with over 1.500 sites in Scandinavia, The Baltics and in Poland. Statoil decided to develop a branded fuel range to further strenghten it’s position as a premier motor fuel provider. Improved fuel launched with the new miles brand. New product, new trademark and new name, requires new design. </p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">A new name in hight performance motor fuels. We designed the logo and visual identity program for the full range of miles and milesPLUS products and grades. We also developed label applications, miles label manual and a miles brand manual to be used as a tool for production and implementation in the European markets.</p>', 219),
(36, 84, 10, '<h5 style="text-align: justify;">Industrial Designer, Stephen Lynch (left) working together with Visual Merchandiser, Espen Tomasgaard (right).  </h5>\n<h1>what process?</h1>\n<h6>By Dag Landewall</h6>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">From time to time, we’re getting questions about our process. Especially from procurement managers in larger corporations. And when we answer that we actually don’t have a standardised process, they tell us that it will be difficult for them to assess our skills. So let’s make it clear: <br><br> We are not built as an agency. Working with us, you will always talk directly to a real expert, not a salesperson. We are big enough to handle rebranding projects for large corporations and small enough to give start-up’s and new players our full attention. </p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br> Bespoke and tailor made. If there is one thing we’ve learned during the years is that no client, no concept and no process is ever the same. That’s why you won’t find any cookie-cutter standardized models here. We found such things insulting to our clients intelligence. Instead, we offer bespoke and tailored services, to suit your specific needs.</p>\n<p> </p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Real insights - real fast. True experts with extensive experience and proven success stories is a powerful combination. We concentrate this into time efficient collaboration to ensure that you get real insights - real fast.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br>Side by side - all the way. We are able to partner with you through every step of your design and implementation process. We are by your side where you need us, all the way from strategy to reality.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If that’s not enough process for you, you may want to talk to the people we’ve worked for or just check out the things we’ve created. Still need a standardized process? Call an agency.</p>', 220);
