(107, 102, 3, '<h5>Reactor team partying alone after Retail Awards hat-trick."Where is everyone? Closing already?"</h5>\n<h1>The hat-trick flip-side</h1>\n<h6>By Dag Landewall</h6>', '<p>Each year the Norwegian advertising industry celebrates itself in many ways with Academy Awards style events. One of them is the Retail Awards (Retailprisen) where a jury of industry experts pick, among other things, the best new retail concepts launched during the year. However, we were among the nominees with three of our 2012 launches; Wyfee, Statoil Highway Minnesund and our new concept for Apotek 1. </p>', '<p>It was of course very funny that all of our concepts came out on top: 01. Wyfee, 02. Statoil and 03. Apotek 1. The flip side of that was that we pretty much had to party alone at the celebrating party afterwards..."Where is everyone? Closing already?"</p>', 0),
