(179, 7, 18, '<h5 style="text-align: justify;">Statoil Fuel &amp; Retail management launching the Miles and Miles Plus quality fuel brand in Lithuainia.</h5>\n<h1>miles for statoil</h1>\n<h6>By Øyvind Nystad</h6>', '<p style="text-align: left;">Statoil Fuel &amp; Retail is the leading service station chain in northern Europe, with over 1,500 sites in Scandinavia, the Baltics and Poland. Statoil decided to develop a branded fuel product line to further strenghten its position as a premier motor fuel provider. The improved fuel was launched with the new miles brand. A new product, new trademark and new name requires a new design. </p>', '<p style="text-align: left;">A new name in high-performance motor fuels. We designed the logo and visual identity program for the full product line of miles and milesPLUS products and grades. We also developed label applications, a miles label manual and a miles brand manual for use as tools with production and implementation in European markets.</p>', 303);
