(188, 102, 10, '<h5>Reactor team partying alone after Retail Awards hat-trick."Where is everyone? Closing already?"</h5>\n<h1>lonely at the top</h1>\n<h6>By Dag Landewall</h6>', '<p style="text-align: left;">Each year the Norwegian advertising industry celebrates itself in many ways with Academy Awards style events. One of them is the Retail Awards (Retailprisen) where a jury of industry experts pick, among other things, the best new retail concepts launched during the year. </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">However, we were among the nominees with three of our 2012 launches; Wyfee, Statoil Highway Minnesund and our new concept for Apotek 1. </p>', '<p style="text-align: left;">It was of course very funny that all of our concepts came out on top: 01. Wyfee, 02. Statoil and 03. Apotek 1. </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">The flip side of that was that we pretty much had to party alone at the celebrating party afterwards..."Where is everyone? Closing already?"</p>', 302),
