(204, 104, 8, '<h5>The Reactor concept for Interfoto received gold at the Norwegian Retail Awards, 2013.</h5>\n<h1>Stay gold 2013</h1>\n<h6>By Dag Landewall</h6>', '<p style="text-align: left;">Also this year the Norwegian advertising industry celebrated itself with  the Retail Awards where a jury of industry experts pick, among other things, the best new retail concepts launched during the year.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">We got the gold for our new concept for destination photo retailer, Interfoto and the silver for our concept for optician chain, Synsam. </p>', '<p style="text-align: left;">We would also like to say congrats to our British competitors, Household Design that where awarded the bonze for their new design for Meny supermarkets. </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">In addition we got a silver in the category "best single marketing actvity/tool" for our customer magazine for Synsam. </p>', 286),
