-selling products clearly displayed.</p>', 271),
(220, 91, 26, '<h5><span>DNB advisor Hanna Folkvord speaks with customer Ingvild U. Halvorsen in the new DNB concept. Photograph by Signe Dons. </span></h5>\n<h1>dnb goes retail</h1>\n<h6>By Inger Guttormsen</h6>', '<p style="text-align: left;"><span>It seemed like a perfect idea at the time: letting banking customers do all the work directly on the Web. Faster and more convenient for the customers - major efficiency gains for the banks. Accordingly, the major banks shut down a  large number of their branches. Is everybody happy now?</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Not quite. Well, this is a story you might have heard before from other sectors, but the major banks focused on fighting each other and simply underestimated the threats from outside the banking sector. In addition, they did not see what mobile pay technologies would do to them either. Estimates are that non-banks will increase their banking market share to 15% in 2020. It was 1.5 % in 2014. In addition, the virtualization of the banking sector made the banks more anonymous and increasingly viewed, by the public, as arrogant and less customer-focused.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">After a few years pf struggling to develop a new real world interaction with their customers, DNB in april 2014 approached Reactor Retail for advice. <span>So what does it take for a bank to become likeable, relevant and useful to today''s consumers? </span></p>', '<p><span>Our approach is that while technology will drive convenience and efficiency, it is personal interaction and physical meeting places that will drive trust. And in banking - trust is perhaps the paramount virtue for anyone with major ambitions.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Retailizing the bank: We created a a people-oriented banking shopping experience that removes physical barriers between customers and staff. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>The ail of the concept is to put the bank and its customers on a partnership level, without the traditional banking powerdressing attitude. It makes people relax and inspires dialog and partnership. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Retailing methology is used for creating an interesting and surprising shopping experience through the use of furniture design, lighting, visual merchandizing tehniques, in-store communcation and product packaging. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>The first pilot was opened at the DNB HQ in Oslo and the second will open in a shopping center location in Oslo in April 2015.</span></p>', 266),
(221, 84, 29, '<h5>Customized and tailor-made. No cookie-cutter standardized models here. Working out communication strategy for Synsam. </h5>\n<h1>for no one but you </h1>\n<h6>By Dag Landewall</h6>', '<p style="text-align: left;">From time to time we receive questions about our process, especially from procurement managers in larger corporations. And when we answer them saying that we actually do not have a standardised process, they then tell us that it will be difficult for them to assess our skills. So we need to make it clear: <br><br> We are not built as an agency. Working with us, you will always talk directly to a real expert, not a salesperson. We are big enough to handle rebranding projects for large corporations and small enough to give start-ups and new players our full attention. </p>\n<p><br> Customized and tailor-made. If there is one thing we have learned during the years, it is that no client, no concept and no process are ever the same. That is why you will not find any cookie-cutter standardized models here.</p>', '<p style="text-align: left;"><span><span>We found such things insulting to the intelligence of our clients. </span>Instead, we offer customized and tailored services, to suit your specific needs.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Real insights - real fast. True experts with extensive experience and proven success stories comprise a powerful combination. We concentrate this into time-efficient collaboration to ensure that you get real insights - real fast.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><br>Side by side - all the way. We are able to partner with you through every step of your design and implementation process. We are by your side where you need us, all the way from strategy to reality.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">If that is not enough process for you, you may want to talk to people we have worked with for or just check out the things we have created. Still need a standardized process? Call an agency.</p>', 304),
